---
import InternalPage from "../../layouts/InternalPage.astro";
import TableOfContents from "../../components/TableOfContents.astro";
import Accordion from "../../components/Accordion.astro";
import AccordionItem from "../../components/AccordionItem.astro";
---

<InternalPage
	heroImage="/uploads/signia-hero.jpg"
	pageSlug="signia"
	title="Signia Hearing Aids"
	description="Commonwealth Audiology provides repair and maintenance services for Signia hearing aids in Georgetown, KY. Contact us to learn more!"
	breadcrumbs={[
		{ label: "Home", href: "/" },
		{ label: "Hearing Aids & Products", href: "/hearing-aids-products/" },
		{ label: "Signia Hearing Aids" },
	]}
>
	<p class="lead-italic">
		Commonwealth Audiology provides repair and maintenance services for Signia
		hearing aids in Georgetown, KY.
	</p>
	<p>
		With more than 140 years of innovation behind them, Signia has built a
		strong reputation for pairing modern design with advanced hearing science.
		Their hearing aids are known for being sleek, discreet, and remarkably
		clear in real-world listening situations.
	</p>
	<p>
		At Commonwealth Audiology, we provide expert service, repairs, and
		maintenance for Signia hearing aids. While we do not dispense Signia
		devices, we are fully equipped to help you care for your technology so you
		continue hearing with comfort, clarity, and confidence.
	</p>
	<p>
		Whether your Signia hearing aids need cleaning, adjustments, repairs, or
		programming support, our experienced audiologist is here to help.
	</p>

	<TableOfContents />

	<h2>Signia Hearing Aid Models We Support</h2>
	<p>Below are Signia models our clinic can adjust, maintain, or troubleshoot.</p>

	<h3>Signia Pure Charge&amp;Go BCT IX</h3>
	<p>
		A stylish receiver-in-canal (RIC) hearing aid with dependable Bluetooth
		Classic connectivity and strong, all-day battery performance.
	</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Universal Bluetooth Classic pairing for reliable streaming</li>
		<li>Up to 36 hours of battery life</li>
		<li>Integrated Xperience (IX) platform with RealTime Conversation Enhancement</li>
		<li>Discreet, modern RIC design</li>
		<li>Telecoil support for looped environments</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Styletto IX</h3>
	<p>
		A slim, elegant device blending fashion-forward design with speech clarity
		and AI-driven personalization.
	</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Portable charging case with up to three days of on-the-go power</li>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming for calls and media</li>
		<li>RealTime Conversation Enhancement for better listening in noise</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Pure Charge&amp;Go IX</h3>
	<p>
		A balanced, everyday RIC option offering advanced speech processing and
		rechargeable convenience.
	</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Direct Bluetooth streaming (phones, TVs, tablets)</li>
		<li>All-day rechargeable battery</li>
		<li>Comfortable, discreet fit</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Silk Charge&amp;Go IX</h3>
	<p>Nearly invisible and ready to wear with soft Click Sleeves, no custom mold required.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Instant-fit comfort</li>
		<li>Clear speech and noise reduction</li>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming support</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Insio IX IIC/CIC</h3>
	<p>Custom-molded options for those wanting the smallest, most discreet in-ear design.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Custom fit for secure comfort</li>
		<li>IIC nearly invisible, CIC extremely discreet</li>
		<li>Remote app control for subtle adjustments</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Pure Charge&amp;Go T AX</h3>
	<p>Built on Signia's AX platform with specialized processing to separate speech and noise.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming for iOS and compatible Android devices</li>
		<li>Signia app controls with Assistant &amp; TeleCare</li>
		<li>All-day rechargeable power</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Styletto AX</h3>
	<p>A slim, modern RIC with strong speech-in-noise performance and intuitive app-based features.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Direct Bluetooth streaming</li>
		<li>Signia app with Assistant &amp; TeleCare</li>
		<li>Portable charging case</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Insio Charge&amp;Go AX</h3>
	<p>Rechargeable custom ITE device built for clarity and reduced listening effort.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming</li>
		<li>App-based support</li>
		<li>Rechargeable all-day battery</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Motion X</h3>
	<p>A powerful, rechargeable behind-the-ear (BTE) option offering long battery life and durability.</p>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Up to 61 hours of use per charge</li>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming (MFi and via StreamLine Mic)</li>
		<li>AI-based Signia Assistant</li>
		<li>Built-in tinnitus therapy</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Signia CROS AX &amp; CROS X</h3>
	<p>For individuals with single-sided deafness.</p>
	<p><strong>Available Styles Include:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>CROS Styletto AX</li>
		<li>CROS Pure Charge&amp;Go AX</li>
		<li>CROS Pure 312</li>
		<li>CROS Silk X</li>
	</ul>
	<p><strong>Unique Features:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li>Bluetooth streaming (Apple/Android on AX platform)</li>
		<li>App control and TeleCare</li>
		<li>My WellBeing activity tracking</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Signia Accessories We Support</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>StreamLine TV</strong> – Direct TV audio streaming</li>
		<li><strong>StreamLine Mic</strong> – Remote microphone + extended Bluetooth options</li>
		<li><strong>StreamLine Remote</strong> – Pocket-sized control device</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Older Signia Models We May Support</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Signia Pure Charge&amp;Go X</li>
		<li>Pure 312 X</li>
		<li>Signia CROS X</li>
		<li>Signia Intuis 3</li>
		<li>Insio Nx</li>
		<li>Pure Nx</li>
		<li>Silk Nx</li>
		<li>Silk Primax</li>
		<li>Pure Primax</li>
		<li>Cellion Primax</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		If you have an older Signia device, our team will evaluate whether repair
		or reprogramming is possible.
	</p>

	<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
	<Accordion>
		<AccordionItem title="What is Signia's most advanced current model?">
			<p>
				Signia's Pure Charge&amp;Go IX (powered by the IX platform), offers
				RealTime Conversation Enhancement, designed to track multiple speakers
				and provide clearer speech in dynamic, noisy environments.
			</p>
		</AccordionItem>
		<AccordionItem title="Can I adjust my Signia hearing aids myself?">
			<p>
				Yes. The Signia app allows you to manage volume, programs, and sound
				balance. Signia Assistant and TeleCare provide guidance and remote
				support between visits.
			</p>
		</AccordionItem>
		<AccordionItem title="Do you repair Signia hearing aids?">
			<p>
				In many cases, yes. We can clean, troubleshoot, reprogram, and complete
				select in-office repairs. If manufacturer service is required, we'll
				guide you through next steps.
			</p>
		</AccordionItem>
	</Accordion>

	<h2>Signia Hearing Aid Care at Commonwealth Audiology</h2>
	<p>
		At Commonwealth Audiology, we're committed to helping you hear comfortably
		and confidently, no matter which brand you use. If you rely on Signia
		technology, we'll provide the ongoing maintenance, adjustments, and expert
		support you need to keep them performing their best.
	</p>
	<p>
		Need service for your Signia hearing aids? <a href="/contact/">Contact Commonwealth Audiology</a> to schedule an appointment.
	</p>
</InternalPage>
